Michelin and Fesvial, sets for wearing the helmet
The Michelin tire manufacturer, in collaboration with the Spanish Foundation for Road Safety (Fesvial), has launched a campaign to encourage helmet wear, mainly among younger motorcyclists, as indicated today by the two structures.
